description:
This is a 37 minute workout called '35-Minute FULL BODY HIIT Workout with Dumbbells (HIITStrong 35, Day 5)' from the channel nourishmovelove.
The workout falls under Cardio/HIIT and Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Advanced and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate and Advanced.
The effort required is Challenging and Extreme.
